                                                                            University and Research) to enrol in a full Italian University program. Appointments for a visa can be requested only upon confirmation of the admission to the entrance exam at
                                                                            an Italian University.  Applicants should always appear in person. All documents must be printed out and presented in original plus a photocopy where required. Applicants
                                                                            must provide: 
