- Proof of accommodation: rental agreement or at least 15/30 days of hotel reservation. In case the applicant is staying with friends/family, a letter of invitation is required
                                                                                    [for a template click here (https://assets.ctfassets.net/xxg4p8gt3sg6/1zdNUF1MUlG2Fh5Taq2sMc/0b36eb850ee1431ac17c7c7736de62ec/proof-of-accomodation.pdf)] along with the host's ID (valid permit of stay for non-European
